# BrighterTeach Frontend Stack
- Framework: Next.js App Router.
- Styling: Tailwind CSS and shadcn/ui.
- Components: Always use functional components and React hooks.
- UX: This is a kid-friendly app. Always preserve the soft pastel colors, rounded corners, and playful UI elements generated by v0.
- State: Rely on local React state (`useState`) and `localStorage`. Do not introduce Redux or external state managers.
